{"tid":1228502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有一絲希望都唔好放棄","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:24:26.000Z","uid":102378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e33995a5e474d5feb0b55ee8bc78554e7d8cf8d","tid":1228502,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"有義士犧牲左<br />\n會有好多人覺得更加無力<br />\n但剩餘既人唔應該犧牲<br />\n我地要繼續撤反惡法 完成義士心願<br />\n其實香港仲未被判死刑，仲有希望<br />\n例如世界各地為我地出聲<br />\n美國為我地行動<br />\n香港人為保衛自由而齊心協力<br />\n求下大家 唔好再犧牲<br />\n我地心痛一次已經好辛苦 <br />\n請大家 繼續為香港作戰 唔好放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正能量 不放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI Can Do It All Day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7898cfb717d5e4ee48d470fe557cc5ee08a6805a","tid":1228502,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/589475668207599620/589501460060831750/unknown.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discordapp.com%2Fattachments%2F589475668207599620%2F589501460060831750%2Funknown.png&h=1434e808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5008ae3465811fc1c30b6b173a69541c0c006afe","tid":1228502,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"Today, we have a chance to take it all back. <br />\n<br />\nYou know your teams, you know your missions. <br />\n<br />\nNo mistakes. No do-overs. <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Be careful. Look out for each other. </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThis is the fight of our lives. And we're going to win. <br />\n<br />\nWhatever it takes. Good luck."},{"pid":"6b74d32572375679833cc28172105c82c9cae212","tid":1228502,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:24:26.000Z","msg":"仲有好多未知之數<img src=\"/assets/fa